title: Avengers - Earth's Mightiest Heroes
description:
NOTHING TO DO WITH THE CARTOON!!!!!

This is the miniseries from a few years back detailing and updating the early Avengers. The first part deals with how the original group turned into Cap's Kooky Quartet, and the second starts right after Vision joined and goes through Wasp and Ant-Man's wedding. A neat mini which I downloaded before, lost, tried to redownload and couldn't find it, and then found on a different drive so I decided to upload. Hope you like.
